@ShepherdsInn_API_HostAddress = https://localhost:7227

### Health check
GET {{ShepherdsInn_API_HostAddress}}/api/health
Accept: application/json


### Submit valid contact message
POST {{ShepherdsInn_API_HostAddress}}/api/contact
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test Person",
  "phone": "(507) 555-1234",
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "preferredContact": "Call",
  "subject": "General Inquiry",
  "message": "This is a test message from the Shepherds Inn website.",
  "website": ""
}


### Submit phone-only contact message
POST {{ShepherdsInn_API_HostAddress}}/api/contact
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Phone Only Test",
  "phone": "(507) 555-1234",
  "email": "",
  "preferredContact": "Call",
  "subject": "Phone Only Inquiry",
  "message": "This is a test message with phone but no email.",
  "website": ""
}


### Submit email-only contact message
POST {{ShepherdsInn_API_HostAddress}}/api/contact
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Email Only Test",
  "phone": "",
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "preferredContact": "Email",
  "subject": "Email Only Inquiry",
  "message": "This is a test message with email but no phone.",
  "website": ""
}


### Invalid: missing both phone and email
POST {{ShepherdsInn_API_HostAddress}}/api/contact
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Invalid Test",
  "phone": "",
  "email": "",
  "preferredContact": "Call",
  "subject": "Invalid Inquiry",
  "message": "This should fail because there is no phone or email.",
  "website": ""
}


### Honeypot spam test
POST {{ShepherdsInn_API_HostAddress}}/api/contact
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Spam Bot",
  "phone": "(507) 555-9999",
  "email": "spam@example.com",
  "preferredContact": "Email",
  "subject": "Spam Test",
  "message": "This should look successful but should not be saved.",
  "website": "https://spam-site.example"
}